data.description: This beautiful Lexington home awaits its next homeowner.This home sits on over one acre in the village limits of Lexington. On the lot also sets a 32 x 24 heated workshop with concrete floors. The current owners have done many updates including creating a 5th bedroom, adding new decking on the back deck, landscaping rocks, and painting the fireplace and so much more. Once inside the home, you will enjoy lots of living space and endless opportunities. The first floor features an office, a large living room with a wood-burning fireplace, and an open-concept kitchen. Upstairs are four well-sized bedrooms, a washer and dryer on the second floor, and a flex space that could be used for many things off of the primary bedroom. Make this your home today!
